1
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,360
"Ashes of Love"

2
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,240
"Episode 27"

3
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:44,520
Mu Ci.

4
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,120
Stop!

5
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,670
Since I can’t grab Spirit-Vanishing Arrow,

6
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:07,050
I can kill Princess of Bian City
as another task to His Majesty.

7
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,920
Mu Ci, will you stay with me

8
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,720
only if I am hurt?

9
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,440
I really went to find you,

10
00:03:09,079 --> 00:03:10,640
but no one knew your whereabouts.

11
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:13,320
In the several hundred years when you disappeared,

12
00:03:15,079 --> 00:03:17,040
I had been waiting for you
at the bank of Wangchuan River.

13
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,120
Are you leaving again?

14
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:29,880
I am not leaving.

15
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:32,960
You haven’t recovered.

16
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,840
Don’t always move.

17
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:36,210
Lie down to have a rest.

18
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:19,760
"Beiyuan Villa"

19
00:04:20,470 --> 00:04:23,640
"Peace reigns over the land"

20
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,440
Your Majesty, it’s late.

21
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:43,680
You should go to bed.

22
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,620
Don’t put off till tomorrow
what should be done today.

23
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,910
I’ll finish the memorials first.

24
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,920
Leave me alone.

25
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:53,400
Yes, I am leaving.

26
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:03,800
Grab Spirit-Vanishing Arrow and kill Xu Feng.

27
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:08,159
Foster mother,
is what you want me to do really right?

28
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,240
Whether the arrow falls or not

29
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,440
depends on my hair.

30
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,840
Is there any good news?

31
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:02,840
I am incompetent and lost Spirit-Vanishing Arrow.

32
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,800
You stayed in the human world for so many days,

33
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:11,640
and you just bring me such a surprise.

34
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:15,800
Your Majesty, His Highness went down
the Human Realm to experience hardships,

35
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,080
which shocked the six realms.

36
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,400
I’m afraid many people

37
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,960
will harm the second Prince.

38
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,480
Who?

39
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,880
Besides Demon Realm,
Snake Fairy Yan You also wants to do so.

40
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,080
I doubt that

41
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,400
he stole Spirit-Vanishing Arrow.

42
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:33,840
When my birthday feast was disturbed last time,

43
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,320
I already doubted

44
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:38,000
Yan You must be related to it.

45
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,520
This time, he made a comeback.

46
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,560
I am afraid the masters
behind Snake Fairy and Rat Fairy

47
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,440
are the same one.

48
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:47,360
You go to investigate who it is.

49
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:51,160
Especially, you need to watch
Water Immortal and Night Immortal carefully.

50
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,840
Night Immortal

51
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:56,480
has gone down the Human Realm
to meet Jin Mi secretly

52
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,800
and destroyed Your Majesty’s plan many times.

53
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,440
Did he do anything bad to Xu Feng?

54
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,600
No.

55
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:06,680
Damned it. Run Yu always goes against me.

56
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,320
He deserves death.

57
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:11,240
You can’t treat him lightly.

58
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:15,280
Has Sui He’s memory been opened?

59
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:19,280
I have been searching for
Spirit-Vanishing Arrow recently,

60
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,720
so I haven’t opened

61
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,080
Princess Sui He’s memory yet.

62
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:24,600
To destroy Jin Mi is important,

63
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:27,600
but you can’t delay opening Sui He’s memory.

64
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,480
If her memory is opened,

65
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:32,720
she can help you in the human world.

66
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,560
You two can make a decision
as the occasion requires.

67
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,400
Yes.

68
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:40,360
Do not let me doubt your value.

69
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:43,200
If you can’t find Spirit-Vanishing Arrow back,

70
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:46,960
I will make another one with your heart blood.

71
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,480
Mu Ci.

72
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:08,600
You haven’t recovered yet.
Why do you walk around?

73
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:11,160
After waking up, I found you were gone.

74
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,600
I thought you had left again,

75
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,200
so I went to look for you.

76
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:18,520
There is no prey on the mountain,

77
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,760
so I went to pick some fruits.

78
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,360
Eat some first.

79
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,920
You haven’t recovered yet,

80
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:36,240
so don’t walk around.

81
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,760
Can you give it back to me now?

82
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,160
You are obedient this time.
I will spare you.

83
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:02,080
Mu Ci, you haven’t told me

84
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:05,840
how you were doing these years.

85
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,120
Where are you going?

86
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,360
I’m going to fetch some water.

87
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,960
You must come back.

88
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,080
I thought you wouldn’t come back.

89
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:14,120
What do you want to eat?
I’m going to cook for you.

90
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,440
Don’t get busy.

91
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:19,960
You have almost fully recovered.

92
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:22,040
If there is nothing else,

93
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,360
you should go back to
Demon Realm as soon as possible.

94
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:29,080
You go back to Demon Realm with me.

95
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:34,240
I can’t go back to Demon Realm again.

96
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:35,680
Why?

97
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,040
Stop asking me.

98
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:39,960
I have changed.

99
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,120
Please don’t be so obsessed with me, Your Highness.

100
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,480
You saved me again and again,

101
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,880
which shows you still care about me.

102
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:50,000
Then why are you so heartless?

103
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:55,640
Because without me,

104
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,400
you can live a better life.

105
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:04,920
Mu Ci.

106
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:26,640
Forget me.

107
00:11:42,470 --> 00:11:44,970
"Yunmeng Lake"

108
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:51,840
On the vast land, ghosts hide in the dark.

109
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:55,360
Above the dense fog, clouds fly.

110
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:56,720
Fog.

111
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:59,160
Fog. Fog.

112
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,000
Fog. Fog.

113
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:07,480
Fog. Fog. Fog.

114
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,840
Good-for-nothing.

115
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,800
You can’t even do the
simplest water and fog skill well.

116
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:23,000
I remember when you were 3,

117
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:25,560
you learned tidal bore skill without teacher.

118
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:28,800
You could tread and move wave and drive torrent.

119
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,360
Why do you become worse now?

120
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,520
Do you deserve to be my son?

121
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,680
Stop crying.

122
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,840
You have made no progress.

123
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:47,400
How can I leave without worry?

124
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,640
Do you know?

125
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:52,200
There are wicked and crafty people

126
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:54,680
who want to kill you for an award outside.

127
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,160
Stop crying.

128
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:58,280
Go.

129
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,280
Master.

130
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:10,880
Yan You, did you make it?

131
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:14,280
I am incompetent,
so I couldn’t grab Spirit-Vanishing Arrow.

132
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,640
Why did you lose?

133
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:19,120
Master,

134
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:22,880
in the cycle of heaven,
the son pays his mother’s debt.

135
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,600
He will be punished.

136
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:27,080
Why not submit to the will of Heaven

137
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:28,640
and let him grow and die
without outside interference?

138
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:33,520
Submit to the will of Heaven?
Grow and die without outside interference?

139
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:36,400
Is this a joke?

140
00:13:36,560 --> 00:13:38,240
I can’t wait for so long.

141
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:41,200
I want him to pay with his life.

142
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,960
General, the lanterns

143
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,960
can be handled by the
Lantern Chief of Shanqin Bureau.

144
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,640
But you are asked to

145
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,600
buy paper and bamboo strips in person.

146
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:55,080
I think His Majesty

147
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:56,640
doesn’t regard you as an outsider at all.

148
00:13:57,800 --> 00:13:58,560
You don’t understand.

149
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:00,240
These are not ordinary lanterns.

150
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:02,160
They are secret weapons

151
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,120
of His Majesty.

152
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:06,720
Of course the best moonlight paper

153
00:14:07,160 --> 00:14:08,560
and toughest bamboo strips must be selected.

154
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:11,240
Weapon? What weapon?

155
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,780
To deal with Liangguo?

156
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,680
Though the opponent is not Liangguo,

157
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:20,240
for His Majesty,

158
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:23,800
it is as hard as a tough battle.

159
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:25,800
Oh, I see.

160
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:29,240
Then you are the best person to do it.

161
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:33,840
It’s late. Let’s go back.

162
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,160
General, general.

163
00:14:45,040 --> 00:14:45,680
Well…

164
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:48,240
We seem to be here just now.

165
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:50,880
I see this tree for the second time.

166
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:52,600
Well…

167
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:56,320
General,

168
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:59,520
did we encounter ghosts?

169
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:01,680
Nonsense. I’m going to find someone to ask.

170
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,480
You wait for me here.

171
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:20,280
Excuse me, I’d like to ask the way.

172
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,480
This time,

173
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:38,320
I will go first.

174
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:47,440
Life is tough.

175
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:52,720
Though you treated me so well all my life,

176
00:15:53,200 --> 00:16:00,640
we can’t avoid sickness and death.

177
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:13,600
If there is next life,
I really don’t want to be human.

178
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:26,120
I only want to be with you forever.

179
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:30,640
I would wait for you.

180
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:40,280
Honey, I feel so bad.

181
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:48,960
Just let me go without pain, OK?

182
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,320
Sir, no!

183
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:04,000
Take the tael silver to buy medicine for aunt.

184
00:17:09,120 --> 00:17:10,880
Are these enough?

185
00:17:17,080 --> 00:17:21,080
Kid, I appreciate your kindness.

186
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:32,720
But I am leaving.

187
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:35,400
Honey,

188
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:40,440
this is a good man.

189
00:17:42,600 --> 00:17:56,800
You must pay him back
if you have the chance in the future.

190
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:01,680
Take…

191
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:07,960
…care.

192
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:42,560
Aunt died a natural death, which is a happy thing.

193
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:45,160
Please restrain your grief.

194
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:48,400
She and I have been together for 60 years.

195
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:54,280
We have never been apart.

196
00:18:55,320 --> 00:19:00,080
The 60 years in human world have gone in a flash.

197
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:02,320
I should go.

198
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:04,640
Where are you going?

199
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:09,400
I’m going to the place I should go.

200
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:11,080
Don’t take it too hard.

201
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:13,320
If you want, you can
go to the military camp with me.

202
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:16,080
We soldiers lost our parents since childhood,

203
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:17,560
and we are willing to support you.

204
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:22,080
Your military camp is right in front.

205
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:24,120
You will get there after taking a turn.

206
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:25,880
Thank you.

207
00:19:26,320 --> 00:19:26,880
Young man,

208
00:19:28,120 --> 00:19:29,640
you are kindhearted.

209
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:33,560
I,

210
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:36,640
I owe you a favor.

211
00:19:37,520 --> 00:19:42,320
If you meet any difficulty in the future,
go to find me with it.

212
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:54,200
General, the old man looks weird.

213
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:56,680
You gave all your money.

214
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:57,920
Will you be cheated?

215
00:19:57,920 --> 00:20:00,840
He doesn’t have children and just lost his wife.

216
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,080
He’s quite poor.

217
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:04,240
How could he

218
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:05,880
bury his dead wife beside a river

219
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:07,360
and leave?

220
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:10,240
In addition, this old woman

221
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:12,200
looks so much older than him.

222
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,800
General, I guess you were cheated.

223
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,920
I don’t plan to get back the money.

224
00:20:17,560 --> 00:20:18,960
Just take it as a good deed.

225
00:20:33,760 --> 00:20:36,320
Aunt, I just met you once.

226
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,760
It’s just a trifle. I dare not accept it.

227
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:42,360
I’ll leave the seal for you.

228
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:44,000
Let’s go.

229
00:20:53,280 --> 00:20:55,880
General, what happened to you?

230
00:21:00,560 --> 00:21:01,480
General.

231
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:30,640
General, did that thing come back again?

232
00:21:30,640 --> 00:21:31,880
I’m going to relieve myself.

233
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:53,040
Damn it. Why does it always go with me?

234
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:55,360
Is it immortal or monster?

235
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,360
Immortals,

236
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:00,800
I have never done any guilty deed

237
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:01,960
and I am open and poised.

238
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:03,800
Since he insisted giving me this gift,

239
00:22:03,920 --> 00:22:06,280
I will accept it.

240
00:22:06,280 --> 00:22:08,400
Please don’t go with me.

241
00:22:12,600 --> 00:22:15,080
Saint Girl of Saint Doctors’ Family

242
00:22:15,080 --> 00:22:17,720
will announce King Yi’s illness.

243
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:23,080
I will ask King Yi to abdicate and choose another wise king.

244
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:24,840
But Minister Fu…

245
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:28,400
If King Yi knows he can’t live long

246
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:30,440
and is unwilling to abdicate,

247
00:22:30,520 --> 00:22:32,090
leaving Huaiwu’s future

248
00:22:32,090 --> 00:22:34,320
and well-being of the people,

249
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:39,240
Minister Fu and others will not agree.

250
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:46,520
What did you say, Dad?

251
00:22:47,280 --> 00:22:48,240
You go back first.

252
00:22:49,080 --> 00:22:50,160
We are leaving.

253
00:22:53,160 --> 00:22:56,360
King Yi is seriously ill
and doesn’t have any child.

254
00:22:57,280 --> 00:23:02,120
He should abdicate and
hand over the regime as soon as possible.

255
00:23:02,120 --> 00:23:04,400
If he dies one day suddenly,

256
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:07,800
the court and the state will be peaceful.

257
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,680
I guess you have planned this for a long time.

258
00:23:10,680 --> 00:23:12,320
I guess the ministers

259
00:23:12,320 --> 00:23:14,440
will recommend you

260
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,440
as the new king tomorrow.

261
00:23:15,440 --> 00:23:18,960
I do so for the future of Huaiwu.

262
00:23:21,680 --> 00:23:24,920
Sui He, I know

263
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,480
your passion for Xu Feng.

264
00:23:26,650 --> 00:23:27,900
But as you can see,

265
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:31,520
even Saint Girl said he couldn’t be saved

266
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:32,480
and would die soon.

267
00:23:32,760 --> 00:23:35,000
Why do you destroy the happiness of your life

268
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:37,160
for such a dying man?

269
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:39,920
Dad, Saint Doctors’ Family
has the best medical skill.

270
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:41,560
As long as Saint Girl is given more time,

271
00:23:41,560 --> 00:23:43,280
she will be able to save my cousin.

272
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:45,640
Why are you so obsessive?

273
00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:47,160
Think about it.

274
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:50,480
