so he is guilty.

333
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:03,320
Please punish him, Your Majesty.

334
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:07,280
Your Majesty, my royalty
could be discerned by the sun and moon.

335
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:08,840
Mr. Liu,

336
00:27:10,280 --> 00:27:13,680
