340
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:22,520
Recently, Saint Girl of Saint Doctors’ Family
went to the palace to treat your illness.

341
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:25,520
We’ll know by asking her.

342
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:30,080
OK. Summon Saint Girl.

343
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:33,120
Summon Jin Mi, Saint Girl of Saint Doctors’ Family.

344
00:27:51,560 --> 00:27:54,680
Jin Mi, Saint Girl of Saint Doctors’ Family
pays a visit to Your Majesty.

345
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,360
Forego the formalities.

346
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:58,920
Thanks, Your Majesty.

347
00:27:59,960 --> 00:28:01,000
Tell me

348
00:28:01,320 --> 00:28:04,440
what illness I have got.

349
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:17,720
Previously, Your Majesty
got up before dawn, ate late and overworked,

350
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:20,560
so he was indeed a little weak.

351
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:27,840
But,

352
00:28:29,840 --> 00:28:31,240
after being nursed by me,

353
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:34,920
Your Majesty is strong and has recovered.

354
00:29:04,280 --> 00:29:07,000
Your Majesty, I’ve received news
from the men sent to Saint Doctors’ Family.

355
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:07,680
How is it?

356
00:29:08,360 --> 00:29:09,560
Everyone of Saint Doctors’ Family is safe.

357
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:11,120
Our men

358
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:13,240
are protecting them well.

359
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:15,920
Duke Nanping’s men all died.

360
00:29:16,760 --> 00:29:19,120
Duke Nanping is always careful and heartless.

361
00:29:20,040 --> 00:29:22,480
Arrange more men to project Saint Girl.

362
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,760
Do not let Duke Nanping

363
00:29:23,760 --> 00:29:25,440
get close to her.

364
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:25,960
Yes.

365
00:29:29,560 --> 00:29:30,960
Previously, you said

366
00:29:31,120 --> 00:29:34,080
Your Majesty’s kidney yang and blood are weak,
so his six yang have problems.

367
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:35,560
As for this,

368
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:39,080
I was indeed inexperienced before,

369
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:41,200
so I made some erroneous judgment.

370
00:29:41,760 --> 00:29:45,960
But these diagnoses are extremely private.

371
00:29:45,960 --> 00:29:48,240
I remember I have never told Your Excellency these.

372
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:51,360
I wonder where Your Excellency got the news.

373
00:29:51,840 --> 00:29:55,240
As Saint Girl, how could you make such an error?

374
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:58,040
How dare you treat Your Majesty slightly?

375
00:29:58,040 --> 00:29:59,240
Your Excellency Duke, please don’t be angry.

376
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:04,120
Your Majesty, I made such an error

377
00:30:04,280 --> 00:30:05,600
because

378
00:30:06,360 --> 00:30:10,120
