381
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:24,640
Most of them are strong drugs of
eighteen incompatibilities and nineteen counteractions.

382
00:30:25,360 --> 00:30:26,920
If Your Majesty takes them for a long time,

383
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,800
