384
00:30:30,280 --> 00:30:33,160
Where is the diet list from?

385
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:34,640
The diet list…

386
00:30:37,040 --> 00:30:38,080
Your Majesty,

387
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:41,320
Saint Girl asked me
about the diet list some days ago.

388
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:45,190
I asked Dong Ruixi, Manager of Food Supervisor,

389
00:30:45,610 --> 00:30:46,650
