390
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:48,160
Now it seems

391
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:51,760
Dong Ruixi is very suspicious.

392
00:30:58,480 --> 00:30:59,960
Summon Dong Ruixi.

393
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:12,200
